sequenceDiagram
    participant Employee as ðŸ‘¤ Employee
    participant Mobile as ðŸ“± Mobile App
    participant API as ðŸŒ Express API
    participant AuthMW as ðŸ” Auth Middleware
    participant ExpenseController as ðŸŽ® Expense Controller
    participant ExpenseService as âš™ï¸ Expense Service
    participant RecurringExpenseController as ðŸŽ® Recurring Expense Controller
    participant RecurringExpenseService as âš™ï¸ Recurring Expense Service
    participant MongoDB as ðŸ—„ï¸ MongoDB
    participant FileStorage as ðŸ“ File Storage
    participant AuditService as ðŸ“‹ Audit Service
